videos.description: Samir Doughty gets the ball in transition and takes it to the rack, finishing through contact for the acrobatic score.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Doughty absorbs contact for tough Auburn bucket) 2020/02/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Doughty absorbs contact for tough Auburn bucket

videos.description: Skylar Mays drives baseline to beat his defender, elevates for the powerful two-handed jam and hangs on the rim after the play.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (LSU's Mays swings on rim after baseline jam) 2020/02/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU's Mays swings on rim after baseline jam

videos.description: Darius Days gets the ball at the top of the key and knocks down his third 3-pointer of the first half, forcing Auburn to call a timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Days fired up after LSU triple) 2020/02/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Days fired up after LSU triple

videos.description: In the closing seconds of the first half, Allen Flanigan grabs a rebound and takes it the other way himself, finishing in transition with an and-1 score.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn closes 1st half with coast-to-coast and-1) 2020/02/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn closes 1st half with coast-to-coast and-1

videos.description: Emmitt Williams comes up with a steal on defense and rises up in transition to flush a one-handed slam all over Auburn's Devan Cambridge.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams throws down major poster slam for LSU) 2020/02/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams throws down major poster slam for LSU

videos.description: J'Von McCormick drives baseline and dishes a sweet cross-court bounce pass to Devan Cambridge in the corner for the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McCormick's beautiful bounce pass sets up Auburn 3) 2020/02/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCormick's beautiful bounce pass sets up Auburn 3

videos.description: Trailing by two with under 30 seconds to play, J'Von McCormick steals the ball away from Skylar Mays and Samir Doughty converts in transition to tie the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn gets steal, score in final seconds to force OT) 2020/02/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn gets steal, score in final seconds to force OT

videos.description: J'Von McCormick dishes to a cutting Isaac Okoro, who elevates for a powerful two-handed jam to extend Auburn's lead in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Okoro flushes thunderous OT slam for Auburn) 2020/02/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Okoro flushes thunderous OT slam for Auburn

videos.description: After Auburn coughs up the lead with less than 10 seconds to play, J'Von McCormick sinks a go-ahead floater to beat the buzzer and lead the Tigers past LSU.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (McCormick's game-winner caps wild finish to Auburn-LSU) 2020/02/08 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: McCormick's game-winner caps wild finish to Auburn-LSU
